Package com.cyberfront.crdt.sample.data

Class SimpleReference

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.cyberfront.crdt.sample.data.AbstractDataType
      • com.cyberfront.crdt.sample.data.SimpleReference
  • public class SimpleReference
extends AbstractDataType
    This is a concrete class type derived from AbstractDataType used to test the CRDT. It manages a reference to another AbstractDataType derived class instances
